"n.制陶；陶器 【英】 n. 制陶 (the work of a potter);陶器 (pots and other objects) 【考】 pottery : shard / bread : crumb(陶器和陶器碎片/面 包和面包屑) n. 陶器(用潮湿粘土成形然后再加热变硬做成的器皿) 【记】pot陶器罐子 【类】pottery: shard = bread: crumb陶器对陶器碎片 = 面包对面包屑 【记】pot 罐, 壶 pottery (n.)  late 15c., ""a potter's workshop,"" from Old French poterie (13c.), from potier (see potter (n.)). Attested from 1727 as ""the potter's art;"" from 1785 as ""potteryware."""
